data.description: Listed by Austin Stiles, KWBH, 605-391-4820. Enjoy the peace of mind of nearly new construction in this split foyer home on an almost 1 acre lot! *Spacious entryway gives access to upstairs, downstairs and the attached garage *Upstairs has a comfortable living room with 10' vaulted ceilings and great natural light *Kitchen and dining areas combine into one functional space with slider door to back yard *Corner kitchen has been upgraded with black stainless steel appliances, good cabinet and counter space and an island for added seating and storage *Primary bedroom in back corner of the home with private access to the main level bathroom *1 additional bedroom and good storage space complete this level *Walkout basement level has a large family room with oversized barn door for easy privacy option, 2 bedrooms with large windows, 1 full bathroom and a separate laundry room with closet storage *Outside has an attached 2-car garage that is insulated and has good storage space *Back yard has a raised multi-level deck that overlooks the fully privacy fenced yard- tons of space for kids, pets, a firepit area or large garden! *Nestled on a corner lot in a growing neighborhood, your next home awaits- call today! **Certain furniture will remain with property at close, contact listing agent for information!
